eNingizimu Afrika (pheqelezi uMzansi) uyizwe ezihloko ze-Afrika. Unenja 2,798 amakhilomitha usebe olwandle iNdiya nolwandle iAthilanthiki. Amazwe enyakatho iNamibhiya, iButswana, iZimbabwe; amazwe empumalanga iMozambiki iSwazi; oSotho uzungelezwa nguMzansi.

Umongameli waseNingizimu Afrika nguJacob Zuma.

uMzansi unesikhundla weholo "phakathi-phezulu" ngokwaBhange Womhlaba, noButswana, noGaboni noMorishisi).[8] Unumnotho umkhulu se-Afrika, amashumi amabili nesishiyagalombili eMhlaba.[9] Ucezu lwesine wenani labantu abasebenzi.[10] Banemali okuncane kuna US $1.25 kosuku.[11]

